Titolo: Clash of Kings

Anno: 2014

Descrizione: Clash of Kings (CoK) is a Chinese mobile massively multiplayer online strategy game developed and published by Elex Tech in 2014. The game has been one of the top grossing apps on the App Store (iOS) and Google Play since its release. The game was downloaded more than 65 million times during its first year on the market. The game used to be playable at Facebook platform with shared cross-platform data until the Adobe Flash support was discontinued.

